   "source": [
    "Q.1- Consider the following diagram: \n",
    "\n",
    "where\n",
    "\n",
    "    a, b, and c are inputs\n",
    "    u = a * b\n",
    "    v = a * c\n",
    "    w = b + c\n",
    "    F = u + v - w\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "What is the value of F? Give answer in the simplest form. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Ans.\n",
    "\n",
    "F = ab+ac-(b+c)\n",
    "   = ab+ac-b-c\n",
    "   = ab-b+ac-c\n",
    "   = b(a-1)+c(a-1)\n",
    "   = (a-1)(b+c)\n",
    " \n",
    "so,\n",
    "F  = (a-1)(b+c)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
